(22,'Oriane Roels','roels.oriane@gmail.com','+32470137653','Belgium','Dear Khumbila team,\r\nYou have been recommended by one of my parent’s friend, the Doctor Pierre to potentially organize a nice trekking for me. I will be assisting to Victor Hugo school in Katmandu from the 19th of April and would be delighted to discover the country side before my stay in Katmandu.\r\nMy particular interests for this trek are some amazing views on some of the giants of the planet, as well as meeting people, the Nepalese culture and as much as possible walking out off beaten tracks. The only constraint are about the timing as I won’t be able to be in Katmandu before the 30th of March and will need to be back on the 18th of April.\r\nI am 18 years old and quite sporty- probably up to level 3 or 4 in a scale of 5.\r\nWould you have any proposal for me – taking into account that I am keen on joining a group to keep control on the expenses?\r\nI hope this information will be relevant for you to propose something but please do not hesitate to contact me should you need any further details.\r\nI look forward to hearing from you.\r\nKind regards,\r\nOriane Roels.\r\n','2020-03-30','max 20 days','1','0','Budget','','2020-01-23 00:01:11'),
